An enclosed research sheet was given  
to a group of 25 children and the     
details which emerged are as follows:-
  1. Gardening and swimming appeared  
to be the favourite leisure activities
of our parents.                       
  2. Some parents' work: Housewife;   
Computer Operator; Health Visitor;    
Heating Engineer; Excavator Driver.   
  3. Amenities most used in the area: 
Playing Fields; Shops; Churches.      
  4. Future changes wanted: Better    
housing; Chemists Shop; Health Centre;
Leisure Centre; Youth Club; Cinema;   
Sports facilities.                    
  5. National Changes wanted: More    
employment; National Service returned;
Capital Punishment; More Hedgerows;   
less pollution etc.                   
  6. Conversations: Family Life;News; 
Unemployment; poverty;football;money; 
politics;drugs;education;violence.
